data.description: Welcome to this delightful home that is ready for its new owners! This lovely home boasts 3 cozy bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, perfect for a growing family or those looking for some extra space. The brand new flooring throughout gives the home a fresh and modern feel, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Situated on an end unit, you'll enjoy privacy and tranquility as you relax in your spacious master bedroom. Step outside to a large yard, ideal for hosting gatherings or enjoying outdoor activities. With all these wonderful features, this home is truly a gem. Come and make this house your new home sweet home!
